CodeBook

Raw data collection
The raw data collection are obtained from: http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones.

Collection

Data set information
The database are obtained from the work done and published by Anguita et al. (2012). The data was collected with a smartphone in order to probe more deeply mathematical models that serve to develop applications for Intelligent Environment systems. Such data was obtained from 30 volunteers while performing moderate activities (such as brisk walking, climbing stairs, sitting, lying down and getting up).

Atribute information

