Raw Data Transformation
the script is designed to substract and organize data for further analysis. The tidy data set must be delivered with Codebook and a ReadMe file writed as Markdown document

Tidy data set
     Variables
The tidy data set contains :
     The tidy data set identifiers:

- Experiment subjects
    - 1-30
- Activity label
    - WALKING, WALKING_UPSTAIRS, WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS, SITTING, STANDING, LAYING
- Mean values for the different variables messured

The final dataset
The final data set are tidy and is written to the file "tidy.txt
